OL,3,CBereaved mother shines light on thread-
OL,4,Cbare probation service
OL,6,FA woman has spoken out about issues in
OL,7,Fthe probation service, more than four
OL,8,Fyears after her daughter and grandson
OL,9,Fwere stabbed to death.
OL,11,FBethany Vincent and her nine-year-old
OL,12,Fson Darren Henson - also known as DJ -
OL,13,Fwere stabbed to death by Bethany's ex-
OL,14,Fpartner Daniel Boulton at their home
OL,15,Fin Louth on 31 May 2021.
OL,17,FAt the time of the murders, Daniel
OL,18,FBoulton was subject to community
OL,19,Forders, bail conditions and a
OL,20,Frestraining order for assaults on
OL,21,FBethany a few months earlier.
