OL,3,CBereaved mother shines light on thread-
OL,4,Cbare probation service
OL,6,FThe review also found scant evidence
OL,7,Fof victim safety planning and said
OL,8,Fstaff over-relied on Boulton's
OL,9,Faccounts in probation meetings, rather
OL,10,Fthan liaising with other key agencies
OL,11,Finvolved. It concluded that overall,
OL,12,F'probation practice in this case was
OL,13,Fnot sufficient' and the assessment of
OL,14,FBoulton's risk should have been
OL,15,Freconsidered.
OL,17,FCaroline Vincent, Bethany's mum, said:
OL,18,F"When you're reading 110 pages of this
OL,19,Fshould have been done, that should
OL,20,Fhave been done, it really is hard to
OL,21,Ftake in.
OL,26,@zD@AOU
