OL,6,F"He'd been in prison before, he'd
OL,7,Fattacked a former girlfriend before,
OL,8,Fkilled his former girlfriend's pet,
OL,9,Fhe'd attacked police officers, he'd
OL,10,Fattacked members of the public, he'd
OL,11,Fhad weapons and threatened people with
OL,12,FBB guns.
OL,14,F"Then (he) met my daughter, attacked
OL,15,Fmy daughter, and they assessed him as
OL,16,Fmedium."
