OL,6,FThe review found that overall the
OL,7,Fprobation practice wasn't sufficient,
OL,8,Fand the assessment of Boulton's risk
OL,9,Fshould have been considered.
OL,11,FIn a statement, a probation service
OL,12,Fspokesperson said: "This was a
OL,13,Fhorrific crime and our thoughts remain
OL,14,Fwith the family and friends of Bethany
OL,15,FVincent and Darren Henson.
