OL,6,FHe joined the inspectorate in March
OL,7,F2024, and has assessed nearly 40
OL,8,Fprobation units since then.
OL,10,FHe said: "Every single unit that I've
OL,11,Finspected since my appointment has
OL,12,Fbeen rated as 'requires improvement'
OL,13,For 'inadequate'. The work they're
OL,14,Fdoing is not good enough.
OL,16,F"I've decided I need to pause my
OL,17,Fprogram and focus on their work on
OL,18,Fpublic protection. We need that work
OL,19,Fto improve urgently."
OL,26,@rD@JOUxD@AOU{D@UO]
