OL,6,FFailure to share information between
OL,7,Fagencies was another issue raised by
OL,8,FMr Jones.
OL,10,FHe said: "Every serious further
OL,11,Foffense that I've ever seen tends to
OL,12,Fbe a failure of information sharing
OL,13,Fbetween agencies.
OL,15,F"Our systems are far too antiquated
OL,16,Ffor a modern world in which
OL,17,Finformation flows through the system.
